    org.tquadrat.foundation.lang.AutoLock.getLock()
    The name getLock() might cause confusion as it is not obviously enough distinguished from AutoLock.lock(). Therefore, it was decided to rename it. Use AutoLock.getWrappedLockInstance() instead.
